{"tid":2031612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，準備好攬炒未？","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T14:31:06.000Z","uid":200122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1ae67b7e1a9020899a1938b921f575a52325a8","tid":2031612,"uid":200122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c94XoytaY9U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc94XoytaY9U&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=8458a74e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c94XoytaY9U</a><br />\n<br />\n【國安法殺到 預備好攬炒未？】<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法無疑再一次證明「一國兩制」從來都只係一個笑話。即使你無參與遊行集會，亦無可能獨善其身，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共已經決心同香港攬炒</strong></span></span>。假如今次先認清中共面目嘅話，希望各位諗清楚下一步應該點做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>「逃避」從來都唔係香港人嘅選擇</strong></span></span>，中共已經撕破畫皮下戰書，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你又準備好攬炒未？</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n調整心態、操Fit啲、見字飲水，為未來做好準備，場仗仲有排打。<br />\n<br />\n#馮達浚 #馮達浚九龍西團隊 #國安法 #攬炒<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n馮達浚 Frankie Fung<br />\n加山傳播創辦人｜半島連線召集人<br />\nCo-founder, DB Channel | Convener, Peninsular Commons"},{"pid":"c108304c0d4661c4cc2c0ba4697fc2163f03f459","tid":2031612,"uid":348453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1e1861e52bd8e441baca0ab3fc6008f8fa1e885","tid":2031612,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"丟掉幻想, 大把和理非驚死 + 黑警戒嚴, 講大遊行果D只係一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳[巴士人鏈]<br />\n限聚令豁免排隊, 黑警分唔到你係咪真排隊搭巴士<br />\n主力部隊集中去頭站, 只要頭站架架車滿載, 中途站上唔到車就可以排隊組人鏈<br />\n排到累去黃店抖吓, 差完電再排過<br />\n畫面夠靚, 岩哂和理非, 有機會上到國際頭版<br />\n<br />\n時間無多, 認同請推post及分享給身邊黃絲朋友<br />\n<br />\nbriefing:<br />\n聽日呢, 9成9人都係行街架啦, 黑警好快就搞亂個場, 俾人驅散後就嘗試叫大家5x聚人, 坐爆5x車, 企爆5x站, 祝大家平安回家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2030973/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2030973/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"eb741ddb6b2cd982182e0acdf9dd4f4c0e07d778","tid":2031612,"uid":3560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"抽擊泛民賣獎券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}